---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
---

<section>
  <h1 class="section-title">Blog di Silvia Genevro</h1>
  <p class="section-subtitle">
    Pensieri, pratiche e suggerimenti su mindfulness, MBSR e vita quotidiana consapevole.
  </p>

  {% if collections.posts and collections.posts | length %}
    <div class="post-list">
      {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
        <article class="post-card">
          {% if post.data.cover %}
            <img src="{{ post.data.cover }}" alt="" class="post-card-cover" />
          {% endif %}

          <h2 class="post-card-title">
            <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
          </h2>

          <div class="post-card-meta">
            Pubblicato il {{ post.date | date("dd MMMM yyyy") }}
          </div>

          {% if post.data.seo_description %}
            <p class="post-card-excerpt">
              {{ post.data.seo_description }}
            </p>
          {% endif %}
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <p>Nessun articolo pubblicato per ora.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>
